      "settings": {
        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"gs-feature-shell\">\n  <section class=\"gs-hero gs-wrap\">\n    <div class=\"gs-hero-copy\">\n      <p class=\"gs-kicker\">Custom In-Ear Monitors</p>\n      <h1>Your Sound,<em>Shaped to You</em></h1>\n      <p class=\"gs-dek\">A custom in-ear monitor is not a louder universal. It is a monitor built around the shape of your ear, tuned to your preference, and finished by hand in our Singapore workshop. The process starts with a pair of ear impressions and ends with a sound that fits no one else.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"gs-hero-media\">\n      <img src=\"{{ 'aaw-ins-hero-ciem-2026.jpg' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"AAW custom in-ear monitors showcasing hand-finished shells and faceplates\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1280\" loading=\"eager\">\n    </div>\n  </section>\n  <div class=\"gs-stat-strip\">\n    <div class=\"gs-wrap gs-stats\">\n      <div class=\"gs-stat\"><b>Singapore Workshop</b><span>Every shell is 3D-printed and hand-finished at 76 Playfair Rd, where we have been building since 2014.</span></div>\n      <div class=\"gs-stat\"><b>Professional Impressions</b><span>We work with audiologists worldwide. A clean, deep impression is the foundation of a monitor that disappears in the ear.</span></div>\n      <div class=\"gs-stat\"><b>2–4 Week Build</b><span>From the day we receive your impressions, most orders ship within two to four weeks, including finishing and QC.</span></div>\n      <div class=\"gs-stat\"><b>Worldwide Shipping</b><span>We ship to over 80 countries. Free local pickup is available at our Singapore showroom.</span></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
