    "gs_steps": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"gs-feature-shell\">\n  <section class=\"gs-section gs-steps-section\">\n    <div class=\"gs-wrap\">\n      <div class=\"gs-steps-head\">\n        <p class=\"gs-kicker\">How It Works</p>\n        <h2>Five steps from order to first listen</h2>\n        <p>The path to a custom monitor is simpler than it sounds. Most of the work happens in our workshop, and we guide you through the parts that need your attention.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"gs-steps-body\">\n        <div class=\"gs-steps-list\">\n          <article class=\"gs-step\">\n            <span class=\"gs-step-num\">01</span>\n            <h3>Place Your Order</h3>\n            <p>Choose your model on our website. Every AAW custom IEM starts with one of our acoustic platforms: from the entry-level A3H+ Lux to the flagship Canary Pro. Add your faceplate design, cable choice, and any personal engraving during checkout.</p>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"gs-step\">\n            <span class=\"gs-step-num\">02</span>\n            <h3>Get Your Ear Impressions Taken</h3>\n            <p>Visit a certified audiologist for silicone ear impressions. The impression needs to capture the full shape of your ear canal and concha, including the second bend. We provide an imprinting guide you can bring to your appointment. At our Singapore showroom, we offer the service at SGD $50.</p>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"gs-step\">\n            <span class=\"gs-step-num\">03</span>\n            <h3>Send the Impressions to Us</h3>\n            <p>Ship your impressions with your order confirmation and adequate protection to our Singapore workshop. If your audiologist offers 3D scanning, you can also send the digital STL or HPS files to support@aaw.me. Either way, we confirm receipt within one business day.</p>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"gs-step\">\n            <span class=\"gs-step-num\">04</span>\n            <h3>Manufacturing Begins</h3>\n            <p>Once your impressions arrive, our lab team 3D-scans them, models your shell geometry, and begins the build. Drivers are installed and crossed over by hand. The faceplate is finished to your specification. Each pair is measured and listened to before it leaves the bench.</p>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"gs-step\">\n            <span class=\"gs-step-num\">05</span>\n            <h3>We Ship Your CIEMs to You</h3>\n            <p>Your completed monitors ship with a carry case, cleaning tool, cable, and documentation. Tracking is provided the moment the package leaves Singapore. Most international deliveries arrive within three to seven business days.</p>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n        <figure class=\"gs-steps-image\">\n          <img src=\"{{ 'canary-pro-ciem-pair.jpg' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"AAW Canary Pro custom in-ear monitor pair with clear shells showing internal drivers\" loading=\"lazy\">\n          <figcaption><b>Custom Canary Pro</b><span>A finished pair with transparent shells, showing the driver layout and faceplate detail.</span></figcaption>\n        </figure>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</div>",
