    "gs_impressions": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"gs-feature-shell\">\n  <section class=\"gs-section dark gs-impressions-section\">\n    <div class=\"gs-wrap gs-grid-2\">\n      <div class=\"gs-impressions-copy\">\n        <p class=\"gs-kicker\">Ear Impressions</p>\n        <h2>The foundation of a perfect fit</h2>\n        <p>An ear impression is a silicone cast of your ear canal and outer ear. It captures the unique shape that no universal tip can fully match. When done well, the resulting monitor sits flush, seals without pressure, and stays put through long sessions.</p>\n        <p>We strongly recommend visiting a professionally certified audiologist for this step. A good impression goes past the second bend of the ear canal and includes the full concha and helix area. An incomplete impression leads to a loose fit, and a remake takes time.</p>\n        <div class=\"gs-note\">\n          <strong>Showroom service available</strong>\n          <p>If you are in Singapore, we offer ear impression taking at our showroom for SGD $50. The process takes about 10–20 minutes. Please have your ears cleared before coming for the best result.</p>\n        </div>\n        <p>If you need help locating an audiologist near you, email us at <a href=\"mailto:support@aaw.me\" style=\"color:#e2b768;\">support@aaw.me</a> and we will do our best to point you in the right direction.</p>\n      </div>\n      <figure class=\"gs-impressions-image\">\n        <img src=\"{{ 'aaw-ins-method-custom-group-2026.jpg' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"Group of AAW custom in-ear monitors showing variety of shell finishes and faceplate designs\" loading=\"lazy\">\n        <figcaption><b>Custom shell variety</b><span>Each pair is built from individual ear impressions, so no two monitors are exactly alike. The shell shape follows your anatomy.</span></figcaption>\n      </figure>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</div>",
